name: Natural Under-Eye Gel Cream Treatment 0.5oz
description: Lightweight eye gel formulated to improve the appearance of dark circles and fine lines while rejuvenating the eye area for a fully refreshed look. Ingredients: Aqua, Glycerin, Lonicera Caprifolium (Honeysuckle) Flower Extract, Lonicera Japonica (Honeysuckle) Flower Extract, Albizia Julibrissin (Silk Tree) Flower Extract, Vitis Vinifera (Grape) Leaf Extract, Centella Asiatica (Gotu Kola) Extract, Lavandula Angustifolia (Lavender) Flower Water, Kaolin, Butylene Glycol, Duratoside, Polysorbate-20
